        <item>
            <title>【开箱】PS5 Pro / PlayStation 5 Pro 港版行货开箱，主机外观详细睇 + 同旧机尺寸、重量比较</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/04/ps5-pro-unboxing/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-unboxing</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/04/ps5-pro-unboxing/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272937</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>PS5 Pro (PlayStation 5 Pro) 将于 2024 年 11 月 7 日正式公开发售。这部最新强化版 PlayStation，将运行 4K 高解像游戏画面时，流畅度由 4K 30fps 增至 4K 60fps，大大提升 4K 游戏体验。另外 PS5 Pro 引入自家 PSSR 由 AI 驱动的光线追踪功能，带来更迫真的游戏画面；主机内置储存亦升级到 2TB。基于厂方限制，今次我们会先同大家开箱，请留意不久之后我们的详细评测，届时我们会为大家实际测试游戏、看看最新 PSSR 光追效果，还有看看主机散热情况。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272961" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03575-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03575-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03575.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p>在 PS5 Pro 外箱我们已看到主机独特的中央格栅设计，游戏机盒背后印有 PS5 Pro 的新增效能，包括：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03501-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03501-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03501.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03505-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03505-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03505-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>PlayStation® 光谱超解析度</strong><br />
使用 AI 增强解析度在 4K 电视上获得超鲜明的影像清晰度，实现超高画质播放，呈现令人惊叹的细节。</p><p><strong>主机效能最佳化</strong><br />
透过支援 VRR、60 Hz 和 120 Hz 显示器，达到更高且更一致的帧率，实现丝滑流畅的游戏体验。</p><p><strong>进阶光线追踪</strong><br />
在您探索精彩绝伦的游戏世界时，透过光线追踪反射、阴影和高品质全域光照，享受全新层次的写实体验。</p><p>仅适用于与 PS5 相比针对 PS5 Pro 进行增强的特定 PS5 游戏。PS5 Pro 增强功能会因游戏而异。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03500-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03500-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03500.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03503-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03503-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03503.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次我们借来主机盒面印有「无光碟版主机」，代表如果想要玩光碟版游戏，就需要另购光碟机。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03506-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03506-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03506.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲盒外亦有注明盒内的内容物</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272947" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03510-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03510-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03510.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲打开盒后，可即时看到所有配件，包括电源线、USB 充电线、HDMI 线、水平式支架、DualSense 无线控制器等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272960" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03511-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03511-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03511-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下方就是 PS5 Pro 本体以及印刷物</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03513-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03513-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03513.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272957" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03525-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03525-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03525.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272956" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272953" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03531-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03531-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03531.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外为安全起见，厂方强烈建议用户在直立摆放时，配合另购的直立支架使用。图中显示的直立支架为另购产品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03582-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03582-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03582.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>今次 PS5 Pro 设计上最为独特就是它的「百叶帘式」中央饰板，它为主机散热带来更好效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03572-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03572-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03572.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272962" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03541-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03541-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03541.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03574-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03574-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03574.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p>再细看游戏主机，你可发现它的体积非常细小，比起 PS5 最原始的第一个版本（非 Slim 版）要瘦得多。实际量度的重量只为 3.056kg，比起原始版 PS5 的 4.482kg 轻上许多。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03563-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03563-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03563.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03606-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03606-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03606-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro 主机重量约为 3.056kg</p><p>看两部机的侧面，全新 PS5 Pro 主机也比较瘦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03570-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03570-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03570.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>看看 PS5 Pro 的灯光效果，整体气氛与早前的 PS5 Slim 版相若，即使在瘦身的主机机身中，仍保留了特色的线条灯光氛围。灯光映照到外围的保护盖上，型式两种灯光效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03587-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03587-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03587.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03584-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03584-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03584.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><h2>影片：PlayStation 5 Pro 机身灯光实试</h2><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="PS5 PRO 机身灯光" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1026105599?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>主机正面全部改成 USB Type-C 插口，共有 2 个。这也迎合好多 PS5 配件，例如无线耳机、第三方手掣都用上 USB 插头的特点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272974 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110455405-694x518.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="518" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110455405-694x518.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110455405.jpg 1205w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03579-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03579-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03579.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>PS5 Pro 机身背后可看到有更大比例的散热口。提供 HDMI、LAN、支援 10Gbps 传输速度的 USB Type-A x2 插口、电源插口以及防盗线插口。PS5 Pro 同样设有增设 SSD 的插槽，由于厂方限制，我们留待下次评测文章继续为大家介绍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272982" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03562-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03562-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03562.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272985" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>根据厂商要求，今日为大家先做了开箱，我们也跟返规矩。真正 PS5 Pro 主机游戏体验、画面实测将会在不久之后的评测文章中刊出，敬请留意！最后再同大家介绍返 PS5 Pro 的详细特点。</p><p>今次 PS5 Pro 强化版游戏主机增加硬件效能，无论在图像清晰度、画面流畅度还是硬体性能方面都取得了显著提升。PS5 Pro 配备了 67% 更多的运算单元（Compute Units），以及 28% 更快的记忆体速度，整体效能提升使游戏渲染速度高达 45%。再加上进阶的光线追踪技术，让画面中的光影反射与折射更加细致，光线速度更是提升了 2 至 3 倍，带来真实而逼真的视觉效果。另外透过 PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution（PSSR）由 AI 驱动的超解像度技术，透过机器学习来增强画质，让 4K 电视上的画面达到超高清晰度，呈现游戏中的精致细节。</p><h2>流畅的游戏体验</h2><p>PS5 Pro 支援 60Hz 和 120Hz 显示器，提供稳定且高效的帧率，适合各类型游戏的流畅操作，尤其在快速动作和射击游戏中更显优势。这项特性还相容于具光线追踪功能的游戏，使玩家可以在 4K 电视上以 60fps 或最高 120fps 体验逼真的视觉和流畅的操作。</p><p>PS5 Pro 配备 2TB SSD，大幅扩充了游戏储存空间，让玩家可以轻松下载并随时启动喜爱的游戏。主机支援最新的 Wi-Fi 7 无线技术，为线上游玩提供更高的频宽和低延迟的连线体验，在多人连线游戏中享受稳定的网路环境，减少延迟问题。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
